plot: Mishka has a problem with tobacco-addiction and refuses to allow Connor to shout Ned dinner under the agreement with Lou, who actually puts them to the dirty dishes. Max tries to stop Boyd going trough with his engagement to Janae, so he's delighted when Steph learns the dumbo hasn't even decided whether to accept, while Karl despairs to hear Boyd spent the watch's price on the diamond ring. Ned can't stop Connor insisting Karl must leave their musical gig, so girls of the right age would be attracted to them youngsters, but as neither dares to tell him, they ask Susan. Connor learns Carmella is really missing and sets out on a search.   Written by  KGF Vissers
